i2p.susi.webmail.pop3

Class DelayedDeleter

  • java.lang.Object
    • i2p.susi.webmail.pop3.DelayedDeleter

  • class DelayedDeleter
extends Object
    Queue UIDLs for later deletion. We send deletions at close time but we don't wait around for the answer. Also, the user may delete mails when offline. So we queue them here and reconnect to delete.
    Since:
    0.9.13
